Package: INLAocc
Title: Occupancy Models via INLA (Laplace Approximation)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Gilles", "Colling", , "gilles.colling@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Fits single-species, multi-species, spatial, temporal, integrated,
    and spatially-varying coefficient occupancy models using Integrated Nested
    Laplace Approximations (INLA). Provides a fast alternative to MCMC-based
    frameworks like 'spOccupancy', with a compatible API including lme4-style
    random effects syntax, posterior predictive checks, WAIC, k-fold
    cross-validation, and design-matrix prediction.
